videoSnippet.title: Nakamura Pushes The Pawn 4 Squares Against a South African Chess Hustler
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Watch the original footage https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xn0TN468yU4

In a visit to South Africa, the local chess hustler community takes on GM Hikaru Nakamura in a speed chess game! Should Nakamura have lost at the end of this game due to an illegal pawn promotion?!

South African Chess Hustler vs Hikaru Nakamura
During his visit to South Africa 
Giuoco Piano Game: Giuoco Pianissimo (C50)

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Nc3 Nf6 4. Bc4 Bc5 5. d3 O-O 6. O-O d6 7. Bg5 h6 8. Bh4 Bg4 9. h3 Bxf3 10. Qxf3 Nd4 11. Qd1 g5 12. Bg3 c6 13. Ne2 Kg7 14. Nxd4 Bxd4 15. c3 Bb6 16. Kh2 h5 17. f3 h4 18. Bf2 Nh5 19. Bxb6 axb6 20. d4 Qf6 21. f4 Nxf4 22. Qg4 Qg6 23. dxe5 dxe5 24. Rf2 Rad8 25. Raf1 b5 26. Bb3 Rd3 27. Rf3 Rfd8 28. Kg1 Rxf3 29. Rxf3 Rd2 30. Rf2 Rxf2 31. Kxf2 Kh6 32. Qf5 Qxf5 33. exf5 Kg7 34. g3 hxg3+ 35. Kxg3 Kf6 36. h4 gxh4+ 37. Kxh4 Kxf5 38. Bxf7 e4 39. Bb3 e3 40. Kg3 Ke4 41. Bc2+ Nd3 42. a4 e2 43. Bxd3+ Kxd3 44. Kf4 e1=Q 45. Kf5 Qe4+ 46. Kf6 bxa4 47. Kg5 Qf3 48. Kg6 Qf4 49. c4 Ke4 50. c5 Ke5 51. Kg7 Qf6+ 52. Kh7 Kf5 53. Kg8 Kg6 54. b3 Qg7#
